  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "4. world—the kingdom of Israel; as in Isa 13:11, Babylon.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "haughty—literally, \"the height\" of the people: abstract for concrete, that is, the high people; even the nobles share the general distress.",
        "children": []
