      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Jeremiah 3:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). The wicked conduct of men, which has caused the earth also to become chanēphâh, is described in three short, rapid, involuntarily excited sentences (compare ",
        "children": []
